msgstr "远程示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:402
msgid "ptool.fs.glob"
msgstr "ptool.fs.glob"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:404
msgid "`v0.2.0` - Introduced. `v0.5.0` - Added the `working_dir` option."
msgstr "`v0.2.0` - 引入。 `v0.5.0` - 新增 `working_dir` 选项。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:407
msgid "`ptool.fs.glob(pattern[, options])` matches filesystem paths using Unix-style glob syntax and returns a string array of matched paths sorted lexicographically."
msgstr "`ptool.fs.glob(pattern[, options])` 使用 Unix 风格 glob 语法匹配文件系统 路径，并按字典序返回命中的路径字符串数组。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:411
msgid "`pattern` (string, required): A glob pattern. Relative patterns are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime directory, so they follow `ptool.cd(...)`."
msgstr "`pattern`（string，必填）：glob 模式。相对模式会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录 解析，因此会受到 `ptool.cd(...)` 的影响。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:413
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Glob options. Supported fields:"
msgstr "`options`（table，可选）：glob 选项。支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:413
msgid "`working_dir` (string, optional): Override the base directory used to resolve relative patterns. Relative `working_dir` values are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime directory."
msgstr "`working_dir`（string，可选）：覆盖相对模式解析时使用的基准目录。 相对 `working_dir` 会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:417
msgid "Returns: `string[]`."
msgstr "返回：`string[]`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:418
msgid "Hidden files and directories are matched only when the corresponding pattern component explicitly starts with `.`."
msgstr "隐藏文件和目录只有在对应模式片段显式以 `.` 开头时才会被匹配。"

